TDD exercise complete. All 7 tests pass:
- empty image returns empty
- scale=1 returns unchanged copy
- single pixel scaled by 2
- single row scaled horizontally
- single column scaled vertically
- multi-row multi-column scaled by 2
- scaled by factor 3

Final implementation in `src/pixel-art-scaler.ts`:
```typescript
const repeat = <T>(value: T, times: number): T[] => Array(times).fill(value);

export const scalePixelArt = (image: string[][], scale: number): string[][] =>
  image.flatMap(row => repeat(row.flatMap(pixel => repeat(pixel, scale)), scale));
```
